Specification description: IAMF v1.1.0
https://aomediacodec.github.io/iamf/v1.1.0.html

[iamf][Rule #0] Error: [Section 3.2] Audio Frame OBU for substream 18 has non-zero num_samples_to_trim_at_start (100) after a frame that was not fully trimmed.

